  "description": "A parody of Robin Hood and Sherlock Holmes in one person, in <i>Robin of Sherlock</i> you find yourself in Sherwood forest where strange things are afoot. Dorothy has been mugged on the Yellow Brick Road, Watson is dead and there is a Kentucky Fried Chicken franchise around the corner. You as the titular hero have to find out who is behind all these sinister things <br><br><i>Robin of Sherlock</i> is a traditional text adventure made using the Quill adventure generation software from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?company=Gilsoft\">Gilsoft</a>. You tell the game what you want to do via a textual interface and the parser is based on a basic verb / noun input.",
